            <div class="title">
                <h2>TripleWave</h2>
                <span class="byline">An open-source tool to bring RDF streams to the Web</span> </div>
            <div id="three-column">
                <div class="boxA">
                    <div class="box"> <span class="fa fa-cogs"></span>
                        <p>Lift Web streams as RDF streams</p>
                    </div>
